Bio-Medicus's board met shortly after receiving the original
bid in mid-May and took no action on the proposal. A
spokesman said that Bio-Medicus's directors will meet to
consider the new proposal. He declined further comment.
   Under a 1987 pact, Medtronic can't boost its current 5.5%
stake in the company above 10% without Bio-Medicus board
approval.
