</IN>
<LP>
   Systems Center Inc., Reston, Va., said it acquired
Software Developments International Pty. Ltd., a developer of
network-management software, in a transaction valued at about
$43.5 million.
   Systems Center, a provider of data-base software, said it
paid about $3.3 million in cash and 1,896,930 shares of its
