<LP>
   SUMITOMO TRUST &amp; BANKING Co. (Tokyo) -- Fumihiko Imamura,
44 years old, previously manager of the company's Los Angeles
office, was named president and chief executive officer of
the New York-based Sumitomo Trust &amp; Banking Co. (U.S.A.)
unit. He succeeds Hirokzu Mizukami, 42, who became general
manager of financial institutions at the home office.
